{"tid":1472011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求高手整份612-721-811報告，DQ警隊","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T02:49:34.000Z","uid":267881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8c2ac500a4639f6392e69d2f2ab682b199e4be","tid":1472011,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇人做呀</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之前開錯台，唔怪之得冇人推</span><br />\n<br />\n勇武街頭陣地戰已不合時宜<br />\n唔想再損失勇武手足，所以一定要變陣<br />\n一係突襲敵營，一係忍術老豆搵仔<br />\n上街集會遊行示威留返俾和理非玩<br />\n<br />\n和理非<br />\n當務之急係眾籌俾法律團隊寫報告<br />\n（即係好似攬抄巴嘅做法咁）<br />\n等份有國際認授性嘅報告一出就出師有名<br />\n全部唔帶黃絲帶嘅警員、之前被記名嘅警員<br />\n即時停薪留職，直至中立獨立調查報告出爐<br />\n如遇反抗即時捉拿<br />\n<br />\n好似林鄭咁一邊談判一邊濫暴，冇衝突架<br />\n我地都可以一邊行私刑一邊砌國際認可嘅聲明<br />\n<br />\n資源：<br />\n<br />\n警隊濫權報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427712\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427712</a><br />\n無牙老虎 監警會質詢警權 警方接受率0%<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1240187\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1240187</a><br />\n國際特赦組織確認香港警察612違反國際人權法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1247785\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1247785</a><br />\n[表揚612指揮官］各警區指揮官及其下屬列表<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1259177\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1259177</a><br />\n一齊推612黑警上國際刑事法庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1249282\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1249282</a><br />\n鏗鏘集721元朗恐襲中+英文官方版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1398116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1398116</a><br />\n官鄉警黑，中共策劃721元朗恐襲證據<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372823\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372823</a><br />\n全球反擊811戰爭罪行！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1452870\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1452870</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他和理非戰線唔好忽視！走出同溫層！<br />\n要同步進行！日日做！<br />\n<br />\n一般文宣-輿論戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460426\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460426</a><br />\n<br />\n輸出革命<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437447\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437447</a><br />\n<br />\n支爆文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437411\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437411</a><br />\n<br />\n諜戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434887\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434887</a><br />\n<br />\n打擊TVB廣告商<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437184\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437184</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該幫推上熱門</span></span>"},{"pid":"57a79d3f63bf393b82429f1de519ddd7919e575a","tid":1472011,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/1